Main pronunciation 主要发音: yí

Other pronunciations 其它发音: Not exists.

Original meaning 本义: Meaning Yi (nationality); tripod, wine vessel; rule

English senses 英语理解:

Usage example 用法举例:

Importance by frequency 常用频率:

Shuowen 说文解字: 宗廟常器也從糸糸綦也廾持米器中寶也彑聲此與爵相似周禮六彝雞彝鳥彝黄彝虎彝蟲彝斚彝以待祼將之禮

Character decomposition 字形分解 [?]:
Compound 彞 from rice 米 mǐ and (rem- 大 dà) from two-hands-below 廾 gǒng and single-thread 糸 mì and (rem- backward-E 彐 jì) from phonetic pig-head 彑 jì .

Decomposition notes 字形分解说明 [?]:
/(a kind of divination in oracle script)
